==Vegoose 2005== Held October 29 and October 30, 2005 at various venues, primarily [[Sam Boyd Stadium]]. Other venues included the [[House of Blues]], ''[[The Joint (music venue)|The Joint]]'' at the [[Hard Rock Hotel and Casino (Las Vegas)|Hard Rock Hotel and Casino]], [[Aladdin Las Vegas|Aladdin]] [[Theatre for the Performing Arts]], and [[Orleans Arena]].
